{"type": "article", "id": 4842, "title": "Next Keyboard 键盘输入法", "description": "", "date": "2014-12-31T08:32:59Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 18, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233751AZtqbzSolWMLkaNn.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t来自加拿大的软件开发公司 Tiny Hearts 日前推出了一款名为「Next Keyboard」的输入法，甚至为其高调地配上了“为 iPhone 准备的完美键盘”这样的广告语。用 iPhone 的人很多，吐槽 iPhone 输入法的人也不少，那这款 Next Keyboard 的优势在何处呢？据设计团队介绍，这款输入法将空格键变为可以滑动的指针条，方便用户编辑文本；一大亮点是其 swipe to type 功能，可以让使用者无需抬起手指就可以完成输入。目前，Next Keyboard 正在 <a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/robjama/next-keyboard-the-perfect-keyboard-for-iphone/\" target=\"_blank\">Kickstarter</a> 上众筹，预计在 2015 年 2 月推出。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233750E1uK8LJvrD5VjQwY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5609375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233750YgmbBAsoKeZCuJfG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5609375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/ksr/assets/003/011/726/cdb6f3551f7a695c27bbb4f8fd85ff30_large.gif?1417755011\" width=\"640\" alt=\"\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/ksr/assets/003/011/706/c2ed2f91a439d06b8d7c5fd4e99deeff_large.gif?1417754673\" width=\"640\" alt=\"\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/ksr/assets/002/998/601/a7d97b5baeae70d262a56330ca3f115b_large.gif?1417546563\" width=\"640\" alt=\"\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/ksr/assets/003/011/708/c0ec2adfc0b78c1cbe26aa54e59632e3_large.gif?1417754705\" alt=\"\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/ksr/assets/003/013/845/72e1ef10b5ae4488c8513d411eb0fc9f_large.gif?1417805248\" width=\"640\" alt=\"\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}